ISLAMABAD, Jul 31 (APP): Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif’s visit to the flood-affected areas of Districts Tank and Dera Ismail Khan on Sunday was deferred due to inclement weather.
The prime minister was scheduled to visit these flood-hit districts of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa to review the ongoing relief and rehabilitation efforts.
